Tiqbilin n '''Ayt Ṣwab''' gant yan mnnaw n tqbilin tisusiyin munin ddu ism n Tmunt n Tqbilin n Ayt Ṣwab, Tamunt ad tetabɛa ula nttat i Tiqbilin n udrar lli illan ɣ Tmunt n Tqbilin n [[Actukn|Wactukn]] Imqqurn. Ɣ iwtta n tqbilt ad ɣ ugmuḍ ar nttafa taqbilt n [[Ida Ugniḍif]] d tqbilt n [[Ammln]], ɣ ugafa ar nttafa taqbilt n [[Ayt Tidli]], ɣ umalu ar nttafa taqbilt n [[Ayt Ḥmad]] d taqbilt n [[Ida Ursmuk]], ɣ iffus ar nttafa taqbilt n [[Ida Usmlal]].<ref>Tiqbilin n Sus : http://www.tribus-de-souss.tk/2008/11/blog-post_4286.html</ref>

Illa ma ittinin mas d '''Ayt Ṣwab''' gan aqbil yumyn mnnawt tqbilin. Yili ma issmrasn ism n "macyaxa" (مشيخة) i tqbilin ad igan ɣ Ayt Ṣwab. ism n "fraction" ɣd ntta ittwasmrs lliɣ tt nn kkan Ayt Ṣwab ddu tnbaḍt n Fṛansa.

Iskr yan ufṛansis ism nns Jean Podeur yan udlis s [[taclḥit]] d [[tafransist]] isman gis imikk n tskla tamiwant n Ayt ṣwab. Adlis ad iga s ism "Textes berbères des Aït Souab ''(Iḍrisn Imaziɣn n Ayt Ṣwab)'' "

