==== Aclḥiy d waɛrab ====
Gmrn yan uclḥi d yan waɛrab, amzn yat tskkurt d yan waɣuct. Lliɣ tn umzn, inna waɛrab lli uclhi : « Bḍu yanɣ tagwmrt-ad. » Inna yas uclḥi : « Ssgrfɣ ak : ad asiɣ taskkurt, tasit kiyyi waɣcut, nɣ d at tasit waɣcut, asiɣ taskkurt, aynna trit. » Ar ittals i wawal-ann, aylliɣ inna-yas waɛrab-lli : «  Ac ka tgul a had lqrufi ? Wllah, mul had ccttab a ma nddih ! »

==== Imikr d bab n tgmmi ====
Idda yan imikr ikcm s tgmmi n yan urgaz ɣ yid. Ur gis illi ma ittakr abla tumzin. Bab n tgmmi izr at lliɣ n ikcm s tgmmi. Ifss, ur as-inni yat. Ikks imikr aqccab nns, iɛmmr-t s tumzin, isrs t. Iddu ar ittmurruy ɣ tgmmi is ra yaf kra n tɣawsa yadnin. Bab n tgmmi yusi aqccab n imikr lli iɛmmr s tmzin, ihḍu-t ɣ yan lmakan. Lliɣ d yuḍa imikr ur d yufi yat, yaf d aqccab lli lah-t. Iddu a iffuɣ ɣ imi. Inna yas d bab n tgmmi : « Iɣ tffuɣt, tqqnt imi. » Inna yas imikr : « Skar asn ɣikad, ad akk ur tqqnt imi. »

